data.description: Beautiful custom home located on Corpus Christi's Southside in one of the few gated communities. Features open floor plan, 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, plenty of storage. Great layout for entertaining, high ceilings, granite countertops, stained concrete floors throughout, and stainless steel appliances. Short commute to grocery stores, shopping, nightlife, and naval air station.
